psychological_arc.arc_description: Started trusting but learned caution through betrayal

story_summary: agent_000 participated in 20 social interactions. They tried cooperating 15.0% of the time, but were betrayed 3 times. These experiences made them more loss-averse (sensitivity: 1.41). Their trust in others diminished to 0.05.
key_insights: Experienced 3 betrayals but kept trying to cooperate
